summary: Do not repost, share/follow my own accounts.  Ask for permission and tag my own IG when you are reposting on IG. Ask for...
caption:
Do not repost, share/follow my own accounts. 

Ask for permission and tag my own IG when you are reposting on IG. Ask for permisson to use in other places where I don’t have an account. Always credit with an active link on sites where I don’t have accounts. 

If you are on VK share from my VK page. If you are on fb share from my own fb page and so on. SHARE.  That’s why I have those pages.

Reposting my art on vk/fb and putting a link to my artstation doesn’t help me that much. Same with ‘made by Ysenna’. It’s even worse when you credit some random reddit post. It doesn’t help me as an artist since all the feedback goes to your post. I don’t know how to explain it clearer. 

If you want to tell on someone for using my art without my consent, you can message me. I won’t tell anyone who you are. Thank you for the awesome people that help me by doing this.

blog.title: Valar Morghulis
blog.description: I'm here mostly for Arya x Jaqen or Jaqarya, if you prefer, amazing fanfiction authors whose stories help me to deal with the damage the showmakers did to Arya and Jaqen storyline, especially Braavos part. Obsessed with Jaqen H'ghar and Arya Stark and the House of Black and White ;) I love Braavos above all and I hope Arya and Jaqen story will be much better in the next book than what we've got so far in the show. I also love Tyrion  Lannister (really hope he'll get better lines next season), Jon Snow and ser Bronn of the Blackwater. I ship Arya and Jaqen, Tyrion and Tysha (I believe there is hope for them in the book) , Jaime and Brienne, Sansa and Sandor though I also like the idea of Sansa reuniting with Tyrion. I believe Rhaegar Targaryen never raped  Lyanna Stark but saved her from awful Robert Baratheon.

summary: OMG!! I was just watching a fanvideo that paralels Ned and Robert, and Jon and Sansa and my heart was about to explode!! The...
body:
OMG!! I was just watching a fanvideo that paralels Ned and Robert, and Jon and Sansa and my heart was about to explode!! The idea of Robert leaving of Ned to rule, as Jon left Sansa!!! And really the relationship between Jon and Sansa developing for them to become the siblings that they never were before, to be siblings like Ned and Robert were!!! Really never seen that paralel before and I felt I was going to explode :)

Also the parallel this artist has done is a few videos that is really beautiful is when Arya is talking about catching cats in King’s Landing and it parallels with Catelyn and there’s this little smile in Ned’s face and it’s the cutest thing!!

summary: what's your wish list that would happen in GOT S8 ep1, ep 2, ep 3,,ep 4, ep5  & ep 6?
question: what's your wish list that would happen in GOT S8 ep1, ep 2, ep 3,,ep 4, ep5  & ep 6?
answer:
Episode 1- Jon and the Dragonstone crew arrive at Winterfell. We get the most epic and deserved Stark reunion of all time with Jon and Arya. Jon and Bran also reunite and I want it to be super emotional since Jon never got to say a proper goodbye to Bran. Dany gets to meet the Starks and the Starks meet Drogon and Rhaegal.


Episode 2- Arya and Dany bond over their love for Jon. Arya tells Dany about Nymeria and she tells Arya about how Drogon came back to her. Arya officially welcomes Dany into her pack and Dany gets the family she deserves. 


Episode 3-6- The White Walkers are defeated and we get some serious bad ass dragon action and battle sequences and Nymeria returns with a pack attack. I want all of our faves to be happy. I just want them all to get some peace and happiness ^.^.
